  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Sirkantahti Hotel is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>A buffet style breakfast is served in the main hotel restaurant each morning, from 7am - 10am, with a great selection of sweet and savoury options including fruit, yoghurt, toast, cereal, bacon, scrambled eggs, tea, coffee and fruit juice. </p>
<p>Each evening you'll have a three course buffet dinner in the Sirkantähti Restaurant, which includes a meat and vegetable options, plus a salad bar. The restaurant is open for dinner from 5pm - 7pm in December and 6pm - 9pm in January and February (times confirmed locally). There is also an onsite Bar &amp; Café which is open from 9am - 1am.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music. Please also note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
