  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Sirkantähti Hotel is in a fantastic location in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, close to the ski slopes with great access to all of the exciting activities and excursions on offer in Finnish <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a>. In the main reception building you'll find a lovely open fireplace and lounge. The Sirkantähti's popular buffet restaurant and bar, where you'll have breakfast and dinner, are are also located here.</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Located close to the resort centre, you have great access to all of the exciting excursions and activities Levi has to offer. Enjoy the well groomed slopes at the Levi Ski Resort or walk through the untouched snowy landscape on a snowshoe excursion. We also offer a range of reindeer, husky and snowmobile <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Excursions">excursions</a> - it is a great way to immerse yourself in the traditional way of life.</p>
<h2>Bar and lounge </h2>
<p>Return from a day of skiing, sledding or snowmobiling and enjoy warming up in front of the lovely fireplace in the main lounge area. After dinner spend some valuable time with friends and family with a drink from the hotel bar. Meals at the Sirkantahti Hotel are served buffet style - so you'll have lots to choose from. </p>
<h2>Cosy and comfortable rooms </h2>
<p>Set across two buildings, the comfortable hotel rooms are nicely furnished and come equipped with everything you need for your stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland.</a> After a day of exploring the Arctic, hang your coats up to dry in the drying cupboard and warm up in your own private sauna - it is a great way to embrace Finnish traditions. Most of the rooms are in the courtyard building which is next to the main building, so you are not far from the hotel facilities. If you're after your own private space check out the <a data-udi="umb://document/c85b627f9f1b47ca86f1395c4fbb9896" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c85b627f9f1b47ca86f1395c4fbb9896}" title="Sirkantahti Apartments">Sirkantähti Apartments</a>.</p>]]></description>
